
'''Tomas Lutuli Brickhill''' (yavutse ku ya 25 Werurwe 1978), ni umukinnyi wa firime, umwanditsi, akaba n'umucuranzi muri [[Zimbabwe]]<ref>https://www.pindula.co.zw/Tomas_Lutuli_Brickhill</ref> .   Yayoboye filime yamenyekanye cyane muri 2017 muri ''Cook Off'' <ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm9615059/</ref>.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 25 Werurwe 1978 i Londere mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] . Se, Paul Brickhill yahoze ari umusirikare wa Zimbabwe (ZIPRA) akaba n'umuvuzi w'abasirikare<ref>https://africalia.be/fr/News-and-press/Paul-Brickhill-A-life-lived-forever?action=converser&var_lang=en&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafricalia.be%2Ffr%2FNews-and-press%2FPaul-Brickhill-A-life-lived-forever</ref>. Kubera iyo mpamvu, yari mu buhungiro mu [[Bwongereza]] icyo gihe Tomas yavutse<ref>https://www.pindula.co.zw/Tomas_Lutuli_Brickhill</ref>. Ariko, nyuma gato y'ubwigenge bwa [[Zimbabwe]], umuryango wasubiye muri [[Zimbabwe]]<ref>https://www.zimbabwesituation.com/news/tag/tomas-brickhill/</ref>.  Nyuma yo kugaruka, ise yayoboye ibihangano n’umuco byiswe 'The Book Café'. Se amaze gupfa muri 2014, Tomas ayoboye Café.  Afite abavandimwe batatu: Liam, Amy na Declan.  Yize mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Prince Edward, Harare kuva 1991 kugeza 1996.<ref>https://m.famousfix.com/list/zimbabwean-film-directors</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Yavuye muri [[Zimbabwe]] mu 1997 yimukira mu [[Bwongereza]] maze yiga muri Surrey Institute of Art ; Design, Ishuri Rikuru rya Kaminuza mu 1999.<ref>https://www.herald.co.zw/europes-biggest-festival-iffr-comes-to-town/</ref>  Yize Filime nyuma akora imirimo itandukanye agerageza kunguka ubumenyi butandukanye muri Surrey arangiza na Bachelor of Arts (BA) muri Cinematography na Film / Video Production muri 2001<ref>https://www.mandy.com/uk/crew/tomas-brickhill</ref>. Hanyuma yigishije amasomo ya firime ya Raindance Film Festival, BBC na VMI imyaka mike<ref>https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p08fvblk</ref>. 

Yatunze kandi Paw Paw Jam Productions, isosiyete ikora ibijyanye n’umuziki nyafurika ndetse no gufata amashusho mu [[Bwongereza]].  Usibye sinema, ni n'umucuranzi aherekejwe n'itsinda 'Chikwata<ref>https://cookoffthemovie.com/actor/tomas-lutuli-brickhill/</ref>'. 

